inHouseMachineId(ActionEvent) - Method in class controller.ModifyPartScreenController
This method is an event handler for the inHouseRadio Button that sets the radioButtonLabel to "Machine ID: " The method also grabs the text from the radioButtonTextField and makes a copy of it that is used to repopulate the text field if the radio button gets toggled back, so the user doesn't need to reenter it.
